  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK479">
<l>aḷavaṟintu vāḻātāṉ vāḻkkai yuḷapōla</l>
<l>illākit tōṉṟāk keṭum</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The prosperity of him who lives without knowing the measure (of his property), will perish, even while it seems to continue.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
